      <p>
        Extreme Tax Masters is a silly visual novel all about working at an
        office as a tax associate. In between chatting with coworkers and
        talking with various clients, play an <em>extreme</em> tax minigame
        where you smash on your keyboard to do taxes. What first seems like an
        ordinary day might just be the most important day of your career. Can
        you become a tax master?
      </p>
